#      * libgee
#      * libuuid
#      * libsoup
#      * vala (not if building from release tarballs)
#      * gupnp-vala (not if building from release tarballs)
#    * Preferences UI:
#      * gtk+
#    * MediaExport:
#      * sqlite3
#  * Run-time:
#    * Definitely needed:
#      * gst-plugins-base
